node.text: ok i’m super soft right now so i’m gonna write a corny message cuz that’s what i do. just wanted to say i’m so so grateful for u and i know i say it all the time but y’all saved my life so many times and i owe everything to u. thank you for always being there for me when i need you most and thank u for being more than fans. you’re genuinely my best friends and i wouldn’t trade my relationship with y’all for the world. watching you grow along side me has been the biggest honor. i love talking to you and hearing about your life and seeing you grow into beautiful human beings with beautiful hearts. i feel like a proud big sister. so excited for the future. also new song ? like in 3 days? I could cry. anyway i’ll leave u alone now. forever & always✨
